    "reviews": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"apotecha-reviews\"><h2 class=\"apotecha-reviews__heading\">Loved by women<br>who care about their hair.</h2><div class=\"apotecha-reviews__grid\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/2261/4403/files/Group_1.jpg?v=1776184689\" alt=\"Customer review\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__body\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__author\"><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__avatar\">S</span><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__name\">Sofia M.</span></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg></div><p class=\"apotecha-review-card__text\">My hair has never felt this soft. After two weeks my hairdresser asked what I changed. The rice protein really makes a difference.</p></div></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/2261/4403/files/ChatGPT_Image_13._apr._2026_18.12.46_1.jpg?v=1776184711\" alt=\"Customer review\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__body\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__author\"><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__avatar\">L</span><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__name\">Louise K.</span></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg></div><p class=\"apotecha-review-card__text\">Finally a shampoo bar that actually lathers well and doesn't leave my hair feeling dry. Plus zero plastic — win win.</p></div></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/2261/4403/files/UGC_unboxing.jpg?v=1776097562\" alt=\"Customer review\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__body\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__author\"><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__avatar\">E</span><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__name\">Emma R.</span></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg></div><p class=\"apotecha-review-card__text\">I've tried so many natural shampoos and this is the first one that actually works on my thick, colour-treated hair. Obsessed.</p></div></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/2261/4403/files/ChatGPT_Image_13._apr._2026_18.29.31.png?v=1776097785\" alt=\"Customer review\" loading=\"lazy\"></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__body\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__author\"><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__avatar\">M</span><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__name\">Maria P.</span></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg></div><p class=\"apotecha-review-card__text\">One bar has lasted me three months. The scent is subtle and natural, not overpowering. Will never go back to bottles.</p></div></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__image\"></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__body\"><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__author\"><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__avatar\">A</span><span class=\"apotecha-review-card__name\">Anna T.</span></div><div class=\"apotecha-review-card__stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><polygon points=\"10,1 12.6,7.4 19.5,7.6 14,12 15.8,18.9 10,15 4.2,18.9 6,12 0.5,7.6 7.4,7.4\"/></svg></div><p class=\"apotecha-review-card__text\">Bought this for my daughter and she loves it. Her hair feels thicker after just a few weeks. We both switched now.</p></div></div></div></div>",
